{"tid":1163022,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【Google禁華為】中国外交部：支持中企用法律捍衛正當權利","createTime":"2019-05-20T08:08:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-20T09:10:51.000Z","uid":184679,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a5273ce66ee96d47b9f922cddf0e2335fcd34a6e","tid":1163022,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T08:08:28.000Z","msg":"路透社周日（19日）引述消息稱，Google已終止與華為部分業務往來，華為智能手機用戶或將無法更新Android作業系統；華為日後推出的新手機，亦無法使用Play Store及Gmail在內的Google程式和服務。<br />\n<br />\n中國外交部發言人陸慷周一（20日）在例行記者會上就事件回應，稱已看到相關報道，注意到有關Google已暫停對華為的軟硬件轉讓業務，並暫停向華為提供有關服務的說法。<br />\n<br />\n陸慷說，中方將正式確認此事，並進一步積極關注事態進展。同時，中方支持中國企業拿起法律武器捍衛自己的正當權利。<br />\n<br />\n（路透社／中國外交部）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/330955/google%E7%A6%81%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%A4%96%E4%BA%A4%E9%83%A8-%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E4%B8%AD%E4%BC%81%E7%94%A8%E6%B3%95%E5%BE%8B%E6%8D%8D%E8%A1%9B%E6%AD%A3%E7%95%B6%E6%AC%8A%E5%88%A9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%2F330955%2Fgoogle%25E7%25A6%2581%25E8%258F%25AF%25E7%2582%25BA-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25A4%2596%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E9%2583%25A8-%25E6%2594%25AF%25E6%258C%2581%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E4%25BC%2581%25E7%2594%25A8%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25BE%258B%25E6%258D%258D%25E8%25A1%259B%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E7%2595%25B6%25E6%25AC%258A%25E5%2588%25A9&d=RsYziF%2F%2FwXRI7aJQ3s5lGZUrr29XULmfQ5XcAAvzh4c%3D&h=283dc704\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/330955/google%E7%A6%81%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%A4%96%E4%BA%A4%E9%83%A8-%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E4%B8%AD%E4%BC%81%E7%94%A8%E6%B3%95%E5%BE%8B%E6%8D%8D%E8%A1%9B%E6%AD%A3%E7%95%B6%E6%AC%8A%E5%88%A9</a>"},{"pid":"b7eb85263ca6a02606ce0299f40d7896b2c8b742","tid":1163022,"uid":64191,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T08:10:36.000Z","msg":"呢個答法，翻譯係中國縮沙"},{"pid":"2